cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.MM

This paper deals with object detection in autonomous driving, which is a common application of computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The use of thermal imaging also involves machine learning techniques (cs.AI) and potentially deep learning (cs.LG). Finally, the analysis of performance on different datasets involves multimedia (cs.MM).
